<h3>Priority 2 (Weeks 2–4): Establish Your Content Cadence</h3>
<p>Time investment: 4–5 hours per week
Impact: Algorithm categorization begins</p>
<ol>
<li>Choose your 2–3 core topics and commit to them for 90 days</li>
<li>Create a content calendar: 3–4 posts per week</li>
<li>Batch-create content: write all posts for the week in one 2-hour session</li>
